-- PODAK CO LTD May Sales Fall 5.23% (Table) : 3537 TT
-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 2012-06-08T10:15:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-08/podak-co-ltd-may-sales-fall-5-23-table-3537-tt.html
PODAK CO LTD (3537)  said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 5.23% to NT$255,855,000 from NT$269,963,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            255,855          269,963    
YOY%              -5.23%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,076,461        1,021,615   
YOY%              5.37%  
=================================================================
 